high_descs: Turn to the left and go to sinks.
Pick up the candle in between the sinks.
Turn left and move to the left sink.
Put the candle in the right cabinet below the sink.
Turn around and go to the other side of the toilet.
Pick up the candle on the back of the toilet.
Go around the toilet and head back to the left sink.
Put the candle in the right cabinet under the sink to the right of the other candle.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles in the cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: walk over to the center of the sinks
pick up the candle between the sink basins
approach the sink to your left
put the candle in the cabinet below the sink
walk over to the side of the toilet
pick up the candle from the back of the toilet
take the candle to the cabinet under the sink on the left
put the candle in the cabinet next to the first one
anns.task_desc: put two candles underneath the sink in the cabinet

high_descs: Turn to the left and then step forward. Turn to the right and face the sinks.
Pick up the candle from the sink counter.
Turn around and step to the left and face the sink.
Open the cabinet under the sink and place the candle inside. Shut the door.
Turn to the right then go forward then turn to the left and go around to the other side of the toilet.
Pick up the candle from the back of the toilet.
Turn to the right then go forward then turn to the left and go around to the other side of the toilet.
Open the cabinet under the sink and place the candle inside.
anns.task_desc: Place two candles under the sink.
